title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Aug 27 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Aug 27 2021
description:
Former NYT journalist Alex Berenson joined the guys to give the latest update on covid data. Some good news for a change -- natural immunity for the win! U.S. plans covid booster shots at six months instead of eight. Large CDC study doesn't support mask mandates in schools. Heading into the weekend, Clay gives Buck golfing advice. SEC tailgating must be seen to be believed.
